latestIgtvVideos.title: Appa missing you.
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
It's been 2 yrs now missing you big time Daddu. even before I could do big things for my dad he left the world and this is a  small video dedication for him.

Like I said some people don't believe in  heroes exist, but they haven't met my dad is all I would say, he wasn't just my hero but from the day 1 he was my god to me in my life. I know these words are not enough to honour my dads figures, but its always nice to tell the world how much we love , respect, like and how much they mean to us in your life. 
Like every person looks up to his dad as a hero you were not just a hero but u were more than the super power god to us. thnk you so much for everything is not enough we will keep ur same name in the society till we are in this world. And we are your sons will take care of mom and leo throughout... i know that your in a better place may your sould REST IN PEACE.
"I am not ashamed to say that no man I ever met was my father's equal, and I never loved any other man as much. He was the most unsung, unpraised, unnoticed, and yet one of the most valuable asset in our family.
TO THE WORLD YOUR A DAD BUT TO ME YOUR THE WORLD.
I am proud to be your son appa.
i am proud to be SELVARAJAN VELU KUMAR.
@asarun123 @dj_notorious_one
I love you Dad💕😘❤️
#sonanddad

Raw beat. Pure soul. When *Chikkama* by Vengayo drops, it’s not just music—it’s a movement. Each bar hits harder when crumping meets the streets, and my energy becomes the rhythm.

I break to express, not impress. Every pop, every freeze carries emotion. Mixing styles like breaking and popping isn’t about showing off—it’s about showing who I am through motion.

This is beauty in chaos. Dance isn’t always clean—it’s wild, gritty, raw. But within that madness is the poetry of a dancer pouring everything out, one move at a time.
